<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: 「Head of Thran Sect」Mo ShuJiu -->
  <RI_Storytellers_ThranShuJiu.label>「喰仙教首」陌书玖</RI_Storytellers_ThranShuJiu.label>
  <!-- EN: Mo ShuJiu is the leader of the Thran Sect, whose own cultivation has reached the rank of a transcendent immortal, with deep and unpredictable strength. She is a ruthless and cool narrator who will slowly and methodically apply a pattern of threats to wear down your nerves. And for her of the Master Forge, forging colonies and knocking out "impurities" is also a pleasure.\n\nNote: Her attacks will be more difficult, and are not suitable for players who seek peaceful development. -->
  <RI_Storytellers_ThranShuJiu.description>陌书玖是喰仙教的教首，本身修为已经达到了地仙境界之上，实力深不可测。她是残酷而冷静的讲述者，会慢慢以有规律的威胁来压垮你的神经，对主修炼器的她来说，锻打殖民地，敲出“杂质”，这也是一种乐趣。\n\n注意：她的袭击难度会更高，不适合追求和平发展的玩家。</RI_Storytellers_ThranShuJiu.description>
  
</LanguageData>